TITLE: Creating Azure DevOps Project with Terraform
DESCRIPTION: Example configuration for creating an Azure DevOps project with custom settings for visibility, version control, and feature toggles. Demonstrates setting up a private Git project with Agile work item template and disabled test plans and artifacts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/terraform-provider-azuredevops/blob/main/website/docs/r/project.html.markdown#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
resource "azuredevops_project" "example" {
  name               = "Example Project"
  visibility         = "private"
  version_control    = "Git"
  work_item_template = "Agile"
  description        = "Managed by Terraform"
  features = {
    testplans = "disabled"
    artifacts = "disabled"
  }
}
```

