TITLE: Creating Azure DevOps Work Item with Basic Configuration in HCL
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a basic Azure DevOps work item using Terraform. It includes creating a project and a work item with essential properties like title, type, state, and tags.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/terraform-provider-azuredevops/blob/main/website/docs/r/workitem.html.markdown#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
resource "azuredevops_project" "example" {
  name               = "Example Project"
  work_item_template = "Agile"
  version_control    = "Git"
  visibility         = "private"
  description        = "Managed by Terraform"
}
resource "azuredevops_workitem" "example" {
  project_id = data.azuredevops_project.example.id
  title      = "Example Work Item"
  type       = "Issue"
  state      = "Active"
  tags       = ["Tag"]
}
```

