TITLE: Creating Managed Identity AzureRM Service Endpoint in Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create an Azure Resource Manager service endpoint using Managed Identity authentication. It includes project creation and service endpoint configuration with Managed Service Identity.
