TITLE: Creating Manual AzureRM Service Endpoint (Subscription Scoped) in Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a manual Azure Resource Manager service endpoint scoped to a subscription using Terraform. It includes creating a project and setting up the service endpoint with service principal credentials.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/terraform-provider-azuredevops/blob/main/website/docs/r/serviceendpoint_azurerm.html.markdown#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
resource "azuredevops_project" "example" {
  name               = "Example Project"
  visibility         = "private"
