TITLE: Configuring Branch Policy for Work Item Linking in Azure DevOps using Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a branch policy for work item linking in Azure DevOps. It sets up a project, a Git repository, and configures the policy with multiple scopes, including exact matching, prefix matching, and default branch matching.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/terraform-provider-azuredevops/blob/main/website/docs/r/branch_policy_work_item_linking.html.markdown#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
resource "azuredevops_project" "example" {
  name = "Example Project"
}

resource "azuredevops_git_repository" "example" {
  project_id = azuredevops_project.example.id
  name       = "Example Repository"
  initialization {
    init_type = "Clean"
  }
}

resource "azuredevops_branch_policy_work_item_linking" "example" {
  project_id = azuredevops_project.example.id

