TITLE: Configuring Azure DevOps Provider with Base64 Encoded Certificate
DESCRIPTION: Terraform configuration demonstrating how to set up the Azure DevOps provider using a base64 encoded certificate string. Shows provider configuration with encoded certificate and required service principal details.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/terraform-provider-azuredevops/blob/main/website/docs/guides/authenticating_service_principal_using_a_client_certificate.html.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
terraform {
  required_providers {
    azuredevops = {
      source  = "microsoft/azuredevops"
      version = ">=0.1.0"
    }
  }
