TITLE: Operation Syntax in EBNF
DESCRIPTION: Defines the grammar for unary and binary operations, including arithmetic, comparison, and logical operators with precedence rules.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/terraform-provider-azuredevops/blob/main/vendor/github.com/hashicorp/hcl/v2/hclsyntax/spec.md#2025-04-23_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: ebnf
CODE:
```
Operation = unaryOp | binaryOp;
unaryOp = ("-" | "!") ExprTerm;
binaryOp = ExprTerm binaryOperator ExprTerm;
binaryOperator = compareOperator | arithmeticOperator | logicOperator;
compareOperator = "==" | "!=" | "<" | ">" | "<=" | ">=";
arithmeticOperator = "+" | "-" | "*" | "/" | "%";
logicOperator = "&&" | "||";
```

