TITLE: Defining HCL Structural Elements in EBNF
DESCRIPTION: EBNF grammar rules for HCL's core structural elements including configuration files, bodies, attributes, and blocks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/terraform-provider-azuredevops/blob/main/vendor/github.com/hashicorp/hcl/v2/hclsyntax/spec.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

